{
  "page": "The Village Hero",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center; font-style: italic;\">The Village Hero</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Nocover.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Nocover.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/48/Nocover.png/200px-Nocover.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"313\" srcset=\"/images/4/48/Nocover.png 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Author</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:United States\">United States</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/English_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:English language\">English</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Series</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dunk_and_Egg\" title=\"Dunk and Egg\">Dunk and Egg</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Genre(s)</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fantasy\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Fantasy\">Fantasy</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Released</th><td>\nTBA</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Preceded&#160;by</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_She-Wolves_of_Winterfell\" title=\"The She-Wolves of Winterfell\">The She-Wolves of Winterfell</a></i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Followed&#160;by</th><td>\nUnknown</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b> <i>The Village Hero</i> </b> is the working title of the fourth or fifth novella in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dunk_and_Egg\" title=\"Dunk and Egg\">Dunk and Egg</a> series. <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> has stated that he does not know which will be finished first, this story or the novella with the working title <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_She-Wolves_of_Winterfell\" title=\"The She-Wolves of Winterfell\">The She-Wolves of Winterfell</a></i>. He has said he will not know more about completing either novella until he has finished <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-NaB_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-NaB-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rssm16122.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rssm16122.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> As of 2014, work on the novella had not yet begun, and the story remained only \"roughed out\" in Martin's head.<sup id=\"cite_ref-NaB_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-NaB-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Martin also has notes and ideas for additional novellas in the series, which may be finished out of chronological order.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Hms_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Hms-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Plot\">Plot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Village_Hero&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Plot\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><i>The Village Hero</i> takes place in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-NaB_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-NaB-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Village_Hero&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-NaB-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-NaB_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-NaB_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-NaB_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Not_a_Blog\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Not a Blog\">Not a Blog</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://grrm.livejournal.com/365715.html\">Dunk &amp; Egg</a>, April 15, 2014</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rssm16122.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rssm16122.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <i><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/16122\">Waterstones Event</a></i> (August 8, 2019).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Hms-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Hms_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Not_a_Blog\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Not a Blog\">Not a Blog</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://grrm.livejournal.com/412015.html?thread=20463983#t20463983\">How many seasons? (March 12th, 2015), reply to comment (March 19th, 2015)</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" st